# Gitattributes — cross-platform line-ending normalization

* text=auto eol=lf
*.png   binary
*.jpg   binary
*.jpeg  binary
*.gif   binary
*.ico   binar
*.svg   binary
*.woff  binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf   binary
*.eot   binary
*.otf   binary
*.sh    text eol=lf

package-lock.json -diff
pnpm-lock.yaml -diff
yarn.lock -diff
